===Etymology===
[[Calque]] from Latin [[carpe diem]].

===Intransitive verb===
'''to [[seize]] [[the]] [[day]]'''
# {{idiom}} [[Enjoy]] the [[present]] and don't [[worry]] about the [[future]]; [[live]] for the [[moment]]; make the most of [[today]].

